headline: GTA Online
subtitle: SAFETY FIRST
content:
They say there are two ways to make it in Los Santos. Armor plating and submachine guns. That’s why no Agency is complete without a Vehicle Workshop to mod your ride.

With six new business-ready vehicles to spec out with Missile Lock-On Jammers, Remote Control Units, and Slick Mines, no one’s going to throw you off course or stand in your way.
